    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，PLC逻辑作为起点，连到执行器控制器。这个控制器是判断节点对吧？那它分出几条路径？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，是判断节点。如果条件满足走'Yes'分支，进入遥测数据流模块；不满足走'No'分支，进入边缘节点做本地处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：PLC逻辑指向执行器控制器，然后分出Yes到遥测流、No到边缘节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，这两个分支最后都要回到PLC逻辑，形成一个闭环控制。遥测流和边缘节点都要连回去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：遥测流直接回PLC逻辑，边缘节点处理完也回PLC逻辑，两条线合并到同一个终点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，合并回去。这样无论是云端遥测还是本地边缘处理，最终都反馈给PLC做下一轮控制决策。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经加上两条返回线。不过我看执行器控制器的判断标签，用'Yes'和'No'是否足够清晰？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "工业场景里这样标注没问题，Yes表示执行器响应成功需要上报遥测，No表示异常或离线需要本地边缘计算。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "理解了。那PLC逻辑节点在图里出现了两次，起点和终点是同一个实体吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "啊，应该是同一个节点，我描述有误。遥测流和边缘节点都回到最初的PLC逻辑，形成循环，不是两个独立节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，现在遥测流和边缘节点都指向同一个PLC逻辑节点，闭环结构完成了。您再看下整体流程？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，就是这个结构。PLC发起控制，执行器判断后分流，成功走遥测上报，失败走边缘处理，最终都反馈回PLC。",
      "elements_involved": [
